---
description: Best practices for using Drizzle ORM with PostgreSQL
globs: 
alwaysApply: false
---
- Define your database schema using Drizzle's type-safe schema definitions.
- Use Drizzle's query builder for type-safe database operations.
- Implement migrations using Drizzle Kit for version control.
- Utilize Drizzle's relations feature for defining and querying relationships.
